data.description: BRAND NEW ROOF, CORNER .5+/- ACRE LOT, UPDATED 4 BEDROOM HOME! FREE INTEREST RATE BUY DOWN FOR FIRST YEAR WHEN YOU USE A PREFERRED LENDER ASK AGENT FOR DETAILS. Make your appointment today to see this beautiful home featuring wood floors in the living, dining, great room & halls. You will love the open kitchen w/work island, gas cooktop, SS appliances, & large pantry. Open casual dining area looks into the large great rm, centered by a floor to ceiling brick fireplace with raised hearth. Nice mud room at back door with work sink, hall tree, and space for dog kennel, or kids sports bags. Bedroom carpet was replaced within the last year, & bathrooms have been updated. Professional landscaped with magnolias, crapes, & azaleas. Preapproved buyers only. Buyer to verify school zones.
